➜内蒙古武术运动协会8月8日在呼和浩特成立
http://www.sohu.com/a/412195184_469808	16857
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200809/0375ca9b419b4198869c38b54e7e1809.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200809/9aa3a7a9b60a4e5c8aea5fb847328410.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200809/6e90dd6f350e47abb2adcb0fdd1e8c99.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200809/71aeb46f8a3c4e29b272083a140f3d61.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
